表格商户主表的代码预览

drop table if exists COMPANY_BASEINFO;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: COMPANY_BASEINFO */
/*==============================================================*/
create table COMPANY_BASEINFO
(
COMPANY_ID char(6) not null,
COMPANY_NAME varchar(64) not null,
COMPANY_TYPE char(4) not null default 'YLFQ',
COMPANY_STATUS char(1) not null,
COMPANY_ADDR_PROVINCE int(6),
COMPANY_ADDR_CITY int(6),
COMPANY_ADDR_DISTRICT int(6),
COMPANY_ADDR varchar(128),
COMPANY_USCC char(18) not null,
COMPANY_FULL_NAME varchar(128) not null,
CORPORATE_NAME varchar(256),
CORPORATE_ID_CODE varchar(18),
CORPORATE_PHONE char(11),
CREATE_TIME datetime not null default CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
UPDATETIME datetime not null default CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
primary key (COMPANY_ID)
);
